      "content": "but there isn't a path forward. how do you redefine success when you've lost the very foundation of your life? it's like trying to rebuild a house after the ground has swallowed it. people don't want the \"new\" me. they just want the person who was disgraced to stay gone. at this point, it feels less like a struggle and more like just... accepting that the end has already happened.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
